Barnes Bay, Viceroy Anguilla Owner, Wins Approval for Auction on July 27

-- B y   M i c h a e l   B a t h o n
-- 
2011-05-19T15:34:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-19/barnes-bay-viceroy-anguilla-owner-wins-approval-for-auction-on-july-27.html
Barnes Bay Development Ltd., owner of
the  Viceroy Anguilla Resort & Residences  on the British West
Indies island of  Anguilla , won court approval to hold a
bankruptcy auction on July 27 with an affiliate of Starwood
Capital Group LLC as the lead bidder.  The case is In re Barnes Bay Development Ltd., 11-10792,
 U.S. Bankruptcy Court , District of  Delaware  (Wilmington).  To contact the reporter on this story:
Michael Bathon in Wilmington, Delaware, at 
 mbathon@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Pickering at   jpickering@bloomberg.net . 